<div type="abstract"><head>Peter III. Haller an Dietrich Hofer [von Lobenstein] zu Sünching</head><p>Peter Haller versichert die Freundschaft des Rats zu Nürnberg mit Dietel Auer.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_233" id="116v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_233_r2l1"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Dyetrich hofer <expan>Ritt<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒu Sünchingen </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_233_r2l2">Mein vvıllig dinſt beuor . Lıeber her hofer / Als Jr mit </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_233_r2l3">mir vnd 
<del rend="strikethrough"> h </del> peter volkmeir nehſt cʒu landſhute als von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_233_r2l4">des Dytell Awers wegen geredt habt etc daſſelb vvir alſo 
<add>von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan></add> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_233_r2l5">
<add><ab facs="#facs_233_r1l1"><expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab></add> an <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> freunde hıe vom Rate bracht <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / dıe <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_233_r2l6">darauff <expan>geantvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> / daʒ ſie cʒu der cʒeit 
<del rend="strikethrough"> and </del> mit dem <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_233_r2l7">dyetell Awer <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> niht wıſſen cʒeſchıcken <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> gute / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_233_r2l8">vnd wo Jch auch <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> erberkeit lieb vnd dinſt beweiſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_233_r2l9">möcht / das tet ich gern / <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> fe </del> in die <expan>ſ<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>ı</expan> Galli / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_233_r2l10">peter haller der <expan>elt<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_233_r2l11"><expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_233" id="116v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Dyetrich Hofer, <expan>ritt<ex>er</ex></expan>,
                        czu Sünchingen </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Mein willig dinst bevor. Lieber her Hofer, als ir mit mir und Peter Volkmeir
                        nehst czu Landshute als von des Dytell Awers wegen geredt habt etc., dasselb
                        wir also <add>von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan></add>
<add><expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan></add> an <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        freunde hie vom rate bracht <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Die
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> uns darauff
                            <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>, daz sie czu der czeit mit dem
                                <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> Dyetell Awer
                            <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> niht wissen cze schicken
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> gute; und wo ich auch
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> erberkeit lieb und dinst beweisen möcht,
                        das tet ich gern. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in die
                                <expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>i</expan> Galli.<lb/>Peter Haller der
                                <expan>elt<ex>er,</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> czu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
